			<p>Hi! I'm the site's creator, Licson Lee. This site is for people to make polls, questionaires and surveys in no time.</p>
			<h4>Motivation</h4>
			<p>Before the creation of PollEndpoint, I have done some online surverys and found most of them not easy to use and hardcoded.</p>
